text: Alga () is a rural locality (a village) in Maximovksky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 206 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 58 km from Sterlitamak, 8 km from Maximovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Alga, Sterlitamaksky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
